Good morning,
On 03/16/2026, the new GE Ascend CT scanner stopped sending images to PACS around 1:00 p.m. During troubleshooting, we learned the AE Title had been turned off on 03/11/2026 by Mr. Sivilaylack, and Radiology was not informed.
